00035 /* **************** SEPARATE RGBA ******************** */
00036 static bNodeSocketTemplate sh_node_seprgb_in[]= {
00037     {   SOCK_RGBA, 1, "Image",          0.8f, 0.8f, 0.8f, 1.0f},
00038     {   -1, 0, ""   }
00039 };
00040 static bNodeSocketTemplate sh_node_seprgb_out[]= {
00041     {   SOCK_FLOAT, 0, "R"},

00043     {   SOCK_FLOAT, 0, "B"},
00044     {   -1, 0, ""   }
00045 };

00047 static void node_shader_exec_seprgb(void *UNUSED(data), bNode *UNUSED(node), bNodeStack **in, bNodeStack **out)
00048 {
00049     out[0]->vec[0] = in[0]->vec[0];
00050     out[1]->vec[0] = in[0]->vec[1];
00051     out[2]->vec[0] = in[0]->vec[2];
00052 }
00053 
00054 static int gpu_shader_seprgb(GPUMaterial *mat, bNode *UNUSED(node), GPUNodeStack *in, GPUNodeStack *out)
00055 {
00056     return GPU_stack_link(mat, "separate_rgb", in, out);
00057 }

00059 void register_node_type_sh_seprgb(bNodeTreeType *ttype)
00060 {
00061     static bNodeType ntype;
00062 
00063     node_type_base(ttype, &ntype, SH_NODE_SEPRGB, "Separate RGB", NODE_CLASS_CONVERTOR, 0);
00064     node_type_compatibility(&ntype, NODE_OLD_SHADING|NODE_NEW_SHADING);
